      <!-- FIFTH PAGE -->
      <section class="fifth-page container">
        <div class="why-this-school">
          <h1>Why St. Colombus Public School?</h1>
          <p>
            At St. Colombus Public School, we go beyond textbooks to nurture
            well-rounded individuals equipped for life. Our educational
            philosophy focuses not just on academic achievement, but on the
            holistic development of every child-intellectually, emotionally,
            physically, and ethically. We create a learning environment where
            curiosity is encouraged, values are instilled, and each student is
            inspired to reach their full potential. Here's what truly sets us
            apart:
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-this-school-card-container">
          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-section-image">
              <img src="/images/holistics.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <h3>Holistic Education Approach</h3>
            <p>
              At Roots Country School, we believe in nurturing the whole child.
              Our curriculum integrates academics, sports, arts, and life
              skills, helping students grow intellectually, emotionally,
              socially, and morally—preparing them for all aspects of life
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-section-image">
              <img src="/images/strong-value.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <h3>Strong Value System</h3>
            <p>
              We are deeply rooted in Indian culture while embracing global
              perspectives. Our students are guided by values such as honesty,
              empathy, respect, and responsibility-forming the foundation of
              their character and future leadership.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-section-image">
              <img src="/images/experience.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <h3>Experienced & Caring Faculty</h3>
            <p>
              Our dedicated team of teachers brings a wealth of experience,
              subject expertise, and a deep commitment to student well-being.
              They provide personalized attention, fostering both academic
              achievement and emotional growth.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-section-image">
              <img src="/images/safe-and-campus.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <h3>Safe and Serene Campus</h3>
            <p>
              Set amidst the scenic hills of Himachal, our eco- friendly campus
              offers a calm and secure environment. Free from distractions, this
              natural setting promotes focused learning, creativity, and peace
              of mind for every student.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="why-card">
            <div class="why-section-image">
              <img src="/images/focus.svg" alt="" />
            </div>
            <h3>Focus on Individua</h3>
            <p>
              We understand that each child is unique. With small class sizes,
              one-on-one mentoring, and continuous performance feedback, we help
              every student discover their strengths and reach their full
              potential.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="why-card">
