                Studies, and Computer Education, along with value-based learning
                and co-curricular activities for balanced growth.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
              <p>What is the admission process at the school?</p>
              <img src="/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="toggle-icon" />
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
