                Admission is simple and direct. Parents need to fill out the
                admission form and pay the admission charges. No entrance test
                or interview is required, and admission is given on a
                first-come-first-served basis, depending on seat availability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
