              <p>Does the school provide transportation facilities?</p>
              <img src="/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="toggle-icon" />
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                Yes, the school offers safe and reliable transport services
                covering Jhajha, Jamui, and nearby villages. Buses are
                well-maintained and managed by trained drivers and attendants to
                ensure student safety and comfort.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
              <p>What facilities does the school provide?</p>
