            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                The school provides modern classrooms, well-equipped
                laboratories, a library, sports grounds, and cultural activity
                spaces. These facilities support academic excellence, physical
                fitness, creativity, and overall personality development of
                students.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
              <p>What is the school's teaching approach?</p>
